Package com.ultreon.bubbles.init

Class Effects

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.bubbles.init.Effects
public class Effects extends Object
Effect Initialization Effect init, used for initialize effects (temporary effects for players / bubbles that do something overtime). For example, the DefenseBoostEffect instance is assigned here.
See Also:
StatusEffect, com.ultreon.hydro.registry.DeferredRegister<StatusEffect>
